<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">Enhance Customer Support via Marketing Techniques</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1001" relname="joint">In the modern day business scenario , the sales and marketing departments are disintegrating</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1003" relname="preparation">and the entire sales procedure has changed .</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1004" relname="span">Unlike what used to happen in the past ,</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="1005" relname="span">these two departments i.e. marketing &amp; sales are now working together</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="5" relname="purpose">to boost up business revenue .</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="1007" relname="span">The sales representatives of your company today have just as much responsibility as your marketers</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="1008" relname="joint">since they not only have to entertain the customers ’ queries</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="1008" relname="joint">but also have to upsell and cross-sell , as a necessary part of their jobs .</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1010" relname="span">Many tools are used by customer support and sales reps these days ,</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="1011" relname="span">which are made</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="11" relname="purpose">for personalizing the experience of your customers .</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1013" relname="span">So , you should take time</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="1014" relname="span">to look into the practices ,</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="14" relname="elaboration">which can help you enhance your customer support department .</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1016" relname="span">Here are a few marketing techniques</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="16" relname="purpose">to help you out :</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="1018" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="1018" relname="joint">Use Marketing Automation .</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="1020" relname="span">You can make use of a tool like marketing automation ,</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="20" relname="elaboration">which can help you gather behavioral data from your prospective customers .</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="1022" relname="span">Doing this will help you creating a comprehensive file of your prospects .</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1024" relname="span">With the help of marketing automation tool , you can enhance your sales intelligence ,</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1025" relname="span">which will let you equip your customer support and sales agents</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="24" relname="purpose">to refine their communication with your customers ,</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="1026" relname="span">a communication</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="26" relname="elaboration">which is purely focused on the customers ’ expectations and needs .</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="1028" relname="preparation">Tap into Social Data .</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1029" relname="span">Apart from collecting behavioral data via tracking tools and marketing automation , you should also lookup social profiles of your prospective customers</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="29" relname="purpose">to find more business for your organization .</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="1031" relname="span">There are many profile lookup tools ,</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="31" relname="elaboration">which help you tap into social data .</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="1033" relname="span">You can conduct in-depth survey</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="33" relname="elaboration">which may include a company ’s size , revenue and much more .</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="1035" relname="same_unit">Tapping into social data</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="1036" relname="span">helps you find a method</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="1037" relname="joint">to personalize the sales pitch</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="1037" relname="joint">and keep your sales process streamlined .</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1039" relname="preparation">Respond instantaneously .</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="1041" relname="condition">Unlike customers from the past , today ’s customers are more demanding ,</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="1041" relname="span">the reason</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="1042" relname="span">being they have too many options</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="42" relname="purpose">to choose from .</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="1045" relname="condition">If you are not efficient enough</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="1045" relname="span">in providing them information regarding your products and/or services ,</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="1046" relname="span">they will never give you a second chance</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="46" relname="purpose">to market .</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="1048" relname="preparation">Earning customers ’ loyalty</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1049" relname="preparation">has become the most difficult task in the modern era for the entrepreneurs ,</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="1051" relname="cause">since brand switching has become common</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="1051" relname="span">due to countless competitors</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="51" relname="elaboration">offering special rates and packages to their customers .</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="54" relname="attribution">According to WebGreeter® , a leading online chat service provider ,</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="1053" relname="span">30-50 percent of overall sales are a result of instantaneous response from the vendor .</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="1049" relname="joint">Let Facebook help you .</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="1057" relname="span">You can enhance your customer support</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="56" relname="means">by asking help from Facebook .</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="1049" relname="joint">You can create your company ’s page on Facebook</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="1049" relname="joint">and advertise about your products , services , promotions , special packages , discount offers and much more .</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1049" relname="joint">This will help your customers know closely about what you have to offer ,</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="1049" relname="joint">and will make them trust you more .</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="1061" relname="span">The leading online chat service and software vendors such as WebGreeter® also offer integration of live chat with your Facebook page</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="1062" relname="joint">in order to entertain your online visitors</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1062" relname="joint">and give them a purely personalized feeling .</segment>
